txt.en: Allow your animal companions to deal devastating damage by supporting them with buffs and healing.

Wild Rage:
 Elemental skills reduce the active cooldown of Sign of the Wild: Rage by 2s.

Coordination: 
 When your animal companion lands a critical strike, your next skill has no induction.
10 Cooldown
Coordination: \nWhen your animal companion lands a critical strike, your next skill has no induction.\nThis effect cannot trigger more than once every 10s.
